Package eu.linksmart.caf.cm.rules

Class Summary
Action An action defined as the RHS of a Rule, as part of a ContextRuleSet, to be installed in the Context Manager.
ContextRuleSet Contains the contents of the Rule Package to be created, includeds Rules, any inline DeclaredFunctions and DeclaredTypes, and also any imports for the Rules.
DeclaredFunction Defines a function declared inline, as part of the ContextRuleSet, that can be called.
DeclaredType Defines a type declared inline in the ContextRuleSet, that can then be used.
Rule Represents a Rule from the ContextRuleSet.
